           1) Active Duty Military End Strength Growth - Child and Youth Programs ................................................................................................. $24,883
           Increases funds to support the active duty military end strength growth. Funding will be used to recruit additional Family Child Care
           (FCC) providers, allow for more non-traditional and specialized hourly programs, secure additional spaces for Military Child Care in
