                     Reflects an increase in Base Support funding to restore baseline funding levels after a one-time decrease in FY 2026 due to a
                     transfer of discretionary funding to be sourced from the Reconciliation Bill (Public Law No: 119-21 - One Big Beautiful Bill Act).

