4) Civilian Pay - Workforce Modernization .................................................................................................................................................... $4,401
Increased funding and manpower (54 FTEs) reflects the alignment of civilian staffing to validated mission requirements pursuant to
Executive Order 14210, implementing the President’s Department of Government Efficiency Workforce Optimization Initiative and the
March 2025 Deputy Secretary of War memorandum. The Air Force conducted comprehensive data-hygiene and manpower-validation
efforts, resulting in a correction where FY2026 staffing levels were set below the Tactical Intelligence and Special Activities Program
established requirements. The FY 2027 request reflects the full requirement necessary to support mission execution and workforce
modernization.

