                     955 Other Costs-Medical Care
                     989 Other Services

                     (FY 2026 Base: $446,549)

                     4) Medical Readiness - Set the Theater (Pacific) ....................................................................................................................................... $28,680
                     Increase funds required medical investments to prepare and sustain five additional clusters with mission ready material, storage, and
                     sustainment, posturing for Air Force to support INDOPACOM operational requirements. Funding enables Agile Combat Employment
                     (ACE) operations in the first and second island chains by bolstering aeromedical evacuation capability requirements to meet the
                     demands of a conflict with a peer competitor. These efforts enable PACAF to be able to execute an ACE scheme of maneuver.

