6) Direct Mission Support - Combating Cartels in the Northern Hemisphere .......................................................................................... $125,263
Increase in funding to support northern hemisphere efforts to combat cartel and narcotics proliferation. Funds will be used to establish
Joint Interagency Task Force-Counter Cartel and required facilities, enhance information technology used in deterring drug-related
threats, and to support military operations against drug trafficking organizations and their operatives in the region.

