7) Direct Mission Support - Homeland Defense Initiatives ...................................................................................................................... $154,392
Increases funding to support the National Defense Strategy's first line of effort to defend the United States Homeland. Funds will be
used to enhance area of responsibility awareness and establish presence through Standing Joint Task Force-Southern Border to
conduct activities within the homeland to address strategic threats, bolster domestic defenses, and fund activities aimed at
safeguarding the sovereignty and territorial integrity of the United States. Additionally, funds support deployment, vehicles utilization,
training, and equipping of personnel across designated National Defense Areas.

