                     1) Active Duty Military End Strength Growth - Officer Training School............................................................................................................ $187
                     Increases funds to support the active duty military end strength growth. The increased funding will cover Officer Training School
                     operating costs to meet increased throughput. These costs include schoolhouse supplies and equipment and travel. The lack of
                     resources will directly impact the officer accessions annual throughput and reduce the capacity to meet officer accession goals. This
